   "source": [
    "# 🚀 Rocket Engine Safety Shutdown System\n",
    "### **Collins Aerospace** | Agentic AI Safety Framework\n",
    "---\n",
    "> **System:** Simple Reflex Agent using LangGraph + LLaMA 3.1 8B (via Groq)  \n",
    "> **Use Case:** Prevent catastrophic failure during launch by monitoring engine temperature  \n",
    "> **Rule:** `If engine_temperature > threshold → Trigger Automatic Shutdown`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 1 — Install Necessary Libraries"
   ]
  },
